text: Jace Lee Norman (born March 21, 2000) is an American actor. He played Henry Hart in the Nickelodeon television show Henry Danger, Game Shakers and Danger Force., Adam Baker in the Nickelodeon movie Splitting Adam and Rufus in Rufus and Rufus 2. == Early and personal life == Jace Norman was born in Corrales, New Mexico. He has an older brother and an older sister. == References == Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from New Mexico Category:American child actors Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Participants in American reality television series
